name: includedCovariateConceptIds
description: A list of concept IDs that should be used to construct covariates.

name: addDescendantsToInclude
description: Should descendant concept IDs be added to the list of concepts to include?

name: excludedCovariateConceptIds
description: A list of concept IDs that should NOT be used to construct covariates.

name: addDescendantsToExclude
description: Should descendant concept IDs be added to the list of concepts to exclude?

name: includedCovariateIds
description: A list of covariate IDs that should be restricted to.

name: longTermStartDays
description: What is the start day (relative to the index date) of the long-term window?

name: mediumTermStartDays
description: What is the start day (relative to the index date) of the medium-term window?

name: shortTermStartDays
description: What is the start day (relative to the index date) of the short-term window?

name: endDays
description: What is the end day (relative to the index date) of the window?

name: sequenceEndDay
description: What is the end day (relative to the index date) of the feature extraction?

name: sequenceStartDay
description: What is the start day (relative to the index date) of the feature extraction?

name: temporalStartDays
description: A list of integers representing the start of a time period, relative to the index date. 0 indicates the index date, -1 indicates the day before the index date, etc. The start day is included in the time period.

name: temporalEndDays
description: A list of integers representing the end of a time period, relative to the index date. 0 indicates the index date, -1 indicates the day before the index date, etc. The end day is included in the time period.
